trations</u> — a screening of videos by Anne-Mie Van Kerckhoven at Werkstattkino. \r\n\r\nStarting at 7.00pm, this one-hour screening will further expose Van Kerckhoven’s work with computer animation, the manipulation of sound, and her unique approach to the documentation of her own work. Organized as part of Van Kerckhoven’s eponymous solo exhibition and publication Serving Compressed Energy with Vacuum, which is on view at Kunstverein München until 14 June 2015. The artist will be in attendance, and will provide occasional commentary during the screening.',''),(893,1,'2015-06-05 11:40:06','2015-06-05 15:57:42',NULL,'Fischer, Friedrich, Schneider',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'fischer-friedrich-schneider',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','<u>Fischer, Friedrich, Schneider</u>\r\n\r\nDeutschland, 1970\r\nDeutsch\r\n48 Seiten\r\nVerlegt Von Kunstverein München e.V. ',''),(894,1,'2015-06-05 11:43:38','2015-06-05 11:43:38',NULL,'Fischer, Friedrich, Schneider',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'fischer-friedrich-schneider',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','<u>Fischer, Friedrich, Schneider</u>\r\n\r\nGermany, 1970\r\nGerman\r\n48 pages\r\n\r\nPublished by Kunstverein München e.V.',''),(895,1,'2015-06-05 12:15:42','2015-06-05 12:16:41',NULL,'Die Akademie',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'die-akademie',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','<u>Die Akademie</u>\r\n\r\nGermany, 1969/1970\r\nGerman\r\n\r\nPublished by Kunstverein München e.V.',''),(896,1,'2015-06-05 12:25:05','2015-06-05 12:25:05',126,'1974',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1974',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',''),(897,1,'2015-06-05 12:25:32','2015-06-05 12:25:32',126,'1974',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1974',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',''),(898,1,'2015-06-05 12:34:37','2015-06-05 16:01:36',NULL,'Mutz Harnest, Fritz Harnest',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'mutz-harnest-fritz-harnest',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','<u>Mutz Harnest, Fritz Harnest\r